This site is devoted to improving education, healthcare, and economic opportunities for everyone through the free exchange of information and skills.  We create better social services by bringing together people with different points of view and building on each other's work. The table below highlights active areas arranged by point of view [[POV]] and by development project.  

Project objectives and results are presented primarily in the form of stories told from the eyes of people who [[:Category:beneficiary|use]] or [[:Category:Provider|provide]] social services and the [[:Category:Advocate|advocates]] or [[:Category:Associate|assistants]] who build and support those services.  The [[Project:Community Portal|community portal]] serves as the primary starting point for participation.  First time visitors may be interested in learning [[UnaMesa:How UnaMesa works|how UnaMesa works]]. 

