== Points of View ==
=== [[:Category:Provider|Providers]] and [[:Category:Beneficiary|beneficiaries]] ===
* Patients and caregivers who need relevant and timely information with more time spent on quality care and less on paperwork
* Students and teachers who need access and availability of course materials
* Farmers and families who want healthy lives
=== [[:Category:Associate|Assistants]] ===
Serve the needs of providers and others through:
* direct support, answering questions online, training
* developing better tools and skills
=== [[:Category:Advocate|Advocates]] ===
Speak on behalf of others to:
* promote the rights and concerns of underserved communities
* establish institutions that build trust

