==Projects==
=== [[SharedRecords]] ===
* Accessing your health records and giving copies to your doctors, nurses, and other people you trust should be simple and secure.  
=== [[TiddlyWiki]] and [[Wiki exchange]] ===
* You can share, highlight and write in the margins of textbooks. Can we do the same with online textbooks?
=== [[MORE Health Today]] ===
* Bringing together groups around the world to create a '''MObile Research and Education''' network that broadcasts regional healthcare and educational programs with realtime feedback and student participation via mobile phones. 
